<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1149132-i-m-a-but-confused-about-the-joe-chip">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I'm a but confused about the Joe Chip money that Runsiter finds at the end of the story. What does that mean or imply? Isn't Runsiter still alive in the real world? Thanks! <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1149132'><a id="like_count_community_question_1149132" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1149132?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">13 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F22590.Ubik">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1149132-i-m-a-but-confused-about-the-joe-chip">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1149132-i-m-a-but-confused-about-the-joe-chip">See all 5 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

