<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link800420" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=800420&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1149132-i-m-a-but-confused-about-the-joe-chip%2Fanswers%2F800420-the-short-answer-the">flag</a>
