              <span id="reviewTextContainer2157400557" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11308620461907562083">I thoroughly enjoyed this story. At first the reading was bumpy, hard to follow, and confusing. But as I got into his style this easily became one of my favorite PKD novels. <br/><br/>The story is unique and is a combination of science fiction and mystery. The writing and attention to detail showcase that PKD truly is a gifted storyteller. I would highly recommend it because of the direct and to-the-point plot. Thanks!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


