      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/62929-ubik">Quotes from Ubik</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;He felt all at once like an ineffectual moth, fluttering at the windowpane of reality, dimly seeing it from outside.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
